<br>
i disagree about the 'uber' group being efficient.  a mid 50's group can get insane xp and clear 3 named worth in grid (not even tov quest equipped).  other area's may be a bit more difficult, but the only thing that really matters in CT is level's IMO.  you can do more stuff if you have a full group of 60's with okay gear, than you can with a buncha 55's in really great gear.<br>
<br>
