<br>
taunt is pitifully easy to handle in xp groups, even CT before taunt fix.  your group just needs to realize that it's their job to keep agro on you; not your job to keep agro from them.  agro control is a group/raid effort, not lone mystical abillities of weapon procs (though they tend to allow more room for error). <p>--------------<Br>
